Sorry.

2
00:00:07,374 --> 00:00:09,009
These are all from the ladies.

3
00:00:09,009 --> 00:00:11,678
They're all very nice to me
and give me things to eat every day.

4
00:00:11,678 --> 00:00:13,880
Right, what was the question for today?

5
00:00:13,880 --> 00:00:15,615
As a secretary to the General Manager,

6
00:00:15,615 --> 00:00:17,384
of course, I have to shield the boss.

7
00:00:18,685 --> 00:00:19,686
Wait a moment.

8
00:00:19,686 --> 00:00:20,954
is there a risk?

9
00:00:21,521 --> 00:00:23,390
Is it a life-threatening risk?

10
00:00:23,390 --> 00:00:24,557
No,

11
00:00:24,557 --> 00:00:25,992
my mom will worry.

12
00:00:27,527 --> 00:00:31,231
Does the company provide
insurance for employees?

13
00:00:31,231 --> 00:00:32,632
It should, right?

14
00:00:32,632 --> 00:00:34,267
How much is insured? What is the content of it?

15
00:00:34,267 --> 00:00:36,736
How much is the compensation amount?
How do we compensate?

16
00:00:38,405 --> 00:00:40,440
Do you think my secretary

17
00:00:40,440 --> 00:00:41,908
would risk his life to protect me?

18
00:00:41,908 --> 00:00:43,743
What kind of assumption is this?

19
00:00:43,743 --> 00:00:45,378
Who came up with these questions?

20
00:00:45,979 --> 00:00:47,347
