23
00:00:56,224 --> 00:01:01,120
<i>♫ Guess which line holds the pass code ♫</i>

24
00:01:01,841 --> 00:01:04,988
<i>♫ Though you're confused, a bit stubborn ♫</i>

25
00:01:04,988 --> 00:01:07,456
<i>♫ Childish and unromantic ♫</i>

26
00:01:07,456 --> 00:01:14,592
<i>♫ You're my destined angel ♫</i>

27
00:01:18,755 --> 00:01:24,710
<i>♫ You're my destined angel ♫</i>

28
00:01:26,536 --> 00:01:28,614
<i>[You Are Mine]</i>

29
00:01:29,322 --> 00:01:31,458
Now is a critical time for the General Manager.

30
00:01:31,458 --> 00:01:32,992
As his secretaries, we should be

31
00:01:32,992 --> 00:01:34,427
a good support team for the boss.

32
00:01:35,695 --> 00:01:37,997
- Shunyu.
- Yes.

33
00:01:37,997 --> 00:01:39,666
When you're with the General Manager,

34
00:01:39,666 --> 00:01:41,534
try to share his burdens.

35
00:01:42,268 --> 00:01:44,104
Yes, I will.

36
00:01:49,175 --> 00:01:51,744
Why are you waiting for me
down here when it's so hot?

37
00:01:51,744 --> 00:01:53,480
You haven't been sleeping much

38
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,981
for the company's platform anniversary,

39
00:01:54,981 --> 00:01:57,050
yet you still find time
to come down and exercise.

40
00:01:57,050 --> 00:01:59,652
How can I comfortably stay in the office
with the AC on all by myself?

41
00:02:02,021 --> 00:02:04,023
Isn't that the pair of pants you wanted?

42
00:02:04,023 --> 00:02:05,825
- Go ask about it.
- I don't want to, you go.

43
00:02:05,825 --> 00:02:07,227
Excuse me…

44
00:02:07,227 --> 00:02:09,129
Sorry, do you need anything?

45
00:02:09,129 --> 00:02:11,431
Sorry, I wanted to ask
about the pants he's wearing,

46
00:02:11,431 --> 00:02:12,999
because my boyfriend he…

47
00:02:12,999 --> 00:02:14,868
- Do you want to buy it for your boyfriend?
- Yes.

48
00:02:14,868 --> 00:02:16,703
Here, take a look.

49
00:02:18,171 --> 00:02:19,739
For our company's platform anniversary,

50
00:02:19,739 --> 00:02:22,075
this pair is the hottest item,
shaping and aerodynamic pants.

51
00:02:22,075 --> 00:02:23,510
I happen to have two DMs here.

52
00:02:23,510 --> 00:02:25,678
You can take a look.

53
00:02:26,446 --> 00:02:28,014
Thank you.

54
00:02:29,115 --> 00:02:31,084
How about it? Shows a great figure, right?

55
00:02:31,084 --> 00:02:32,619
It's really nice.

56
00:02:32,619 --> 00:02:35,355
It uses German imported
seamless machine design,

57
00:02:35,355 --> 00:02:36,389
one piece formation.

58
00:02:36,389 --> 00:02:38,391
In terms of stretchability,

59
00:02:38,391 --> 00:02:39,592
shaping power, fitness, or comfort,

60
00:02:39,592 --> 00:02:41,561
it all far surpasses other brands.

61
00:02:41,561 --> 00:02:45,365
The new intelligent aerodynamic yarn

62
00:02:45,365 --> 00:02:47,133
automatically senses body temperature,

63
00:02:47,133 --> 00:02:49,302
opens air holes, and releases heat.

64
00:02:49,302 --> 00:02:50,570
Most importantly,

65
00:02:50,570 --> 00:02:53,640
it has both men's and women's styles.

66
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:55,375
Look at this modern two-piece cut.

67
00:02:55,375 --> 00:02:58,478
It looks good in any color combination.

68
00:02:58,478 --> 00:02:59,646
More importantly,

69
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:02,448
it's sold in both online and offline stores.

70
00:03:03,850 --> 00:03:05,084
Baby, let's go buy them now.

71
00:03:05,084 --> 00:03:06,252
Okay, let's go.

72
00:03:08,721 --> 00:03:10,023
How was that?

73
00:03:10,023 --> 00:03:11,157
I remembered it very well, right?

74
00:03:11,658 --> 00:03:12,959
Do you want to switch
to the Promotion Department?

75
00:03:12,959 --> 00:03:14,060
You remembered it so clearly.

76
00:03:14,561 --> 00:03:16,996
No, I happened to glance at the DM.

77
00:03:18,164 --> 00:03:19,299
Oh, my DM.

78
00:03:20,833 --> 00:03:22,468
As long as you've checked it.

79
00:03:23,870 --> 00:03:25,471
To reward you for being so diligent,

80
00:03:25,471 --> 00:03:27,040
tonight,

81
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,141
OT with extra dishes.

82
00:04:08,917 --> 00:04:10,848
<i>[One Week Later]</i>

83
00:04:11,851 --> 00:04:13,052
General Manager,

84
00:04:14,020 --> 00:04:15,688
here are the documents you wanted.

85
00:04:15,688 --> 00:04:17,123
Go home now.

86
00:04:19,459 --> 00:04:21,527
I don't want to be accused
of abusing employees,

87
00:04:21,527 --> 00:04:23,263
so please go home now.

88
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:25,565
Don't worry, General Manager,

89
00:04:25,565 --> 00:04:27,200
I'm in great health. No need to worry.

90
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:28,434
Who told you I'm worried?

91
00:04:29,202 --> 00:04:31,971
Have you ever thought about how much damage
it would cause the company

92
00:04:31,971 --> 00:04:33,806
