93
00:04:34,874 --> 00:04:36,709
I'm sorry, General Manager.

94
00:04:36,709 --> 00:04:38,044
I didn't think it through.

95
00:04:38,044 --> 00:04:39,312
So please, right now, immediately…

96
00:04:39,312 --> 00:04:40,413
That's right.

97
00:04:40,413 --> 00:04:42,649
I'll put on the mask right now.

98
00:04:59,132 --> 00:05:00,433
Don't worry, General Manager.

99
00:05:01,434 --> 00:05:05,038
I definitely won't infect you.

100
00:05:07,540 --> 00:05:09,008
So considerate.

101
00:05:17,016 --> 00:05:18,084
What's next on the schedule?

102
00:05:18,618 --> 00:05:21,321
Next, we're going to a meeting
at Director Chen's company.

103
00:05:26,259 --> 00:05:28,428
You said you wanted to share the workload,

104
00:05:28,428 --> 00:05:29,729
but you can't stand
working overtime for a week.

105
00:05:34,834 --> 00:05:35,968
General Manager,

106
00:05:35,968 --> 00:05:37,770
I'm fine.

107
00:05:39,238 --> 00:05:40,540
First, put on the mask.

108
00:05:42,709 --> 00:05:44,510
You're not going to a meeting.

109
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:46,713
You're dragging everyone down to catch a cold.

110
00:05:46,713 --> 00:05:48,314
Forget it, just go home.

111
00:05:49,115 --> 00:05:50,817
General Manager, it's just a minor cold.

112
00:05:50,817 --> 00:05:52,151
It was an order.

113
00:05:53,019 --> 00:05:55,054
I will have the General Secretary accompany me
to Director Chen's meeting.

114
00:05:56,756 --> 00:05:57,792
Get in.

115
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:08,468
Get in.

116
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:21,714
Take him home directly.

117
00:06:21,714 --> 00:06:22,816
Yes.

118
00:06:23,416 --> 00:06:25,785
Remember to buy him a bowl
of hot porridge on the way.

119
00:06:25,785 --> 00:06:26,848
Yes.

120
00:06:27,954 --> 00:06:29,389
Call me when you get home.

121
00:06:32,458 --> 00:06:34,060
Okay, I'll leave first.

122
00:06:49,475 --> 00:06:50,576
Where is he?

123
00:06:53,179 --> 00:06:54,647
He didn't even close the door.

124
00:07:22,208 --> 00:07:24,640
<i>[Where are you?
I told you to rest, not ignore me.]</i>

125
00:07:25,378 --> 00:07:26,946
Unread and no reply.

126
00:07:26,946 --> 00:07:28,548
Getting bolder, huh?

127
00:07:38,391 --> 00:07:40,026
- General Manager.
- Lisa.

128
00:07:40,026 --> 00:07:41,828
Is Yao in the Secretary's Office now?

129
00:07:41,828 --> 00:07:43,162
I don't see him.

130
00:07:43,162 --> 00:07:44,564
He's not working in there?

131
00:07:46,265 --> 00:07:48,201
Did he take a leave today?

132
00:07:48,201 --> 00:07:50,403
General Manager,
Yao Shunyu didn't take leave today.

133
00:07:50,403 --> 00:07:52,104
Shall we call and check on him?

134
00:07:54,273 --> 00:07:56,476
No need, he's been working hard these days.

135
00:07:56,476 --> 00:07:57,710
Let him rest well.

136
00:07:59,979 --> 00:08:01,581
He had a bit of a cold yesterday.

137
00:08:01,581 --> 00:08:03,983
Handle his work for him.

138
00:08:19,699 --> 00:08:21,200
Yang, where are you?

139
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:23,302
Hi, Boss, I'm eating out.

140
00:08:23,302 --> 00:08:24,804
How was Yao's condition

141
00:08:24,804 --> 00:08:26,005
when he got home yesterday?

142
00:08:26,005 --> 00:08:28,541
As the car couldn't get into the alley,

143
00:08:28,541 --> 00:08:30,076
I only took Mr. Yao to the alley entrance.

144
00:08:30,076 --> 00:08:31,777
I told you to take him home.

145
00:08:31,777 --> 00:08:33,212
But you only took him to the alley.

146
00:08:34,176 --> 00:08:35,283
I'm sorry, General Manager.

147
00:08:35,283 --> 00:08:37,817
Yesterday, when I got back to the car
after buying the porridge, Mr. Yao...

148
00:08:53,599 --> 00:08:54,600
Call Yao Shunyu.

149
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,335
Call him until he picks up.

150
00:08:56,335 --> 00:08:58,571
Send me his home address

151
00:08:58,571 --> 00:09:00,139
- and his family's phone number.
- Yes.

152
00:09:01,641 --> 00:09:02,688
Hello.

153
00:09:03,709 --> 00:09:04,744
General Manager.

154
00:09:04,744 --> 00:09:06,579
Do you want to take this call?

155
00:09:13,452 --> 00:09:14,654
I warn you.

156
00:09:14,654 --> 00:09:16,322
The General Manager of Xia Shi Group,

157
00:09:16,322 --> 00:09:18,824
Xia Shangzhou is now in my hands.

158
00:09:18,824 --> 00:09:20,126
If you dare to call the police, it's over.

159
00:09:20,126 --> 00:09:23,429
I demand a ransom of a hundred million.

160
00:09:24,230 --> 00:09:26,599
Otherwise, wait to collect the body.

161
00:09:26,599 --> 00:09:27,733
You've got it wrong.

162
00:09:27,733 --> 00:09:29,101
I'm really not Xia Shang...

163
00:09:29,101 --> 00:09:31,704
I'm warning you, don't hurt him.

164
00:09:32,672 --> 00:09:34,206
That voice…

165
00:09:34,206 --> 00:09:35,575
It was Shunyu.

166
00:09:35,575 --> 00:09:36,909
He's been kidnapped.

167
00:09:36,909 --> 00:09:38,411
Quickly, call the police.

168
00:09:38,411 --> 00:09:40,313
We can't call the police. If we do, it's over.

169
00:09:40,313 --> 00:09:42,715
If the kidnappers find out
they got the wrong person,

170
00:09:42,715 --> 00:09:44,717
- will they kill him?
- Shut up.

171
00:09:45,718 --> 00:09:46,953
Calm down first.

172
00:09:47,820 --> 00:09:49,021
- Lisa.
- Yes.

173
00:09:49,021 --> 00:09:51,557
Is Yao Shunyu's phone company issued?

174
00:09:52,058 --> 00:09:53,559
Yes.

175
00:09:53,559 --> 00:09:56,228
Right, we can track his phone's location.

176
00:09:58,798 --> 00:10:00,366
I know where he is now.

177
00:10:00,366 --> 00:10:01,467
I'm heading over there right now.

178
00:10:01,467 --> 00:10:04,604
- Call the police.
- Wait, it's dangerous for you to go alone.

179
00:10:07,106 --> 00:10:08,641
Hurry up and call the police.

180
00:10:14,780 --> 00:10:15,915
Don't.

181
00:10:18,084 --> 00:10:19,136
What are you doing?

182
00:10:21,420 --> 00:10:23,389
What are you doing, young man?

183
00:10:37,236 --> 00:10:39,105
No, you've got it all wrong, sir.

184
00:10:39,105 --> 00:10:40,740
I'm not General Manager Xia Shangzhou.

185
00:10:40,740 --> 00:10:42,742
I'm his secretary, Yao Shunyu.

186
00:10:42,742 --> 00:10:44,977
Listen, people like you,

187
00:10:44,977 --> 00:10:46,312
all of them

188
00:10:46,312 --> 00:10:47,847
say they're not the one who's been kidnapped.

189
00:10:48,347 --> 00:10:49,782
You even want to drag your employees into this.

190
00:10:49,782 --> 00:10:52,451
How shameless.

191
00:10:52,451 --> 00:10:54,553
No, sir, I'm telling the truth.

192
00:10:54,553 --> 00:10:56,389
Really, I can prove it.

193
00:10:58,891 --> 00:11:00,192
Take a look in my pocket.

194
00:11:00,192 --> 00:11:01,761
There's my work ID.

195
00:11:01,761 --> 00:11:03,763
It has my name and photo on it.

196
00:11:03,763 --> 00:11:05,031
My name is Yao Shunyu.

197
00:11:09,001 --> 00:11:10,403
Sorry.

198
00:11:10,403 --> 00:11:11,871
Oh, it tickles.

199
00:11:12,538 --> 00:11:14,006
Sorry.

200
00:11:14,006 --> 00:11:16,976
I'm telling you, don't try any tricks.

201
00:11:20,279 --> 00:11:21,414
Yao Shunyu.

202
00:11:24,550 --> 00:11:26,352
You're not Xia Shangzhou?

203
00:11:26,352 --> 00:11:29,021
I'm really not Xia Shangzhou.

204
00:11:29,021 --> 00:11:31,190
Really, sir, if you don't believe me,

205
00:11:31,190 --> 00:11:32,992
you can look it up.

206
00:11:55,581 --> 00:11:57,783
How did I grab the wrong person?

207
00:11:57,783 --> 00:11:58,951
I…

208
00:12:02,288 --> 00:12:04,890
Why am I so unlucky?

209
00:12:11,263 --> 00:12:13,933
Sir.

210
00:12:13,933 --> 00:12:15,267
Are you okay?

211
00:12:16,902 --> 00:12:20,139
Just two days ago, I received this urgent job.

212
00:12:20,139 --> 00:12:24,043
My boss just gave me your company's address,
license plate number,

213
00:12:24,043 --> 00:12:26,345
and a photo, that's all.

214
00:12:26,345 --> 00:12:27,680
And how much did he give me?

215
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:30,249
100,000. I did all this for 100,000.

216
00:12:30,249 --> 00:12:31,283
I'm really...

217
00:12:31,817 --> 00:12:34,487
Lele, Daddy is useless.

218
00:12:36,188 --> 00:12:38,224
Daddy doesn't have a job.

219
00:12:38,224 --> 00:12:41,660
I can't make money
to take you to the doctor, Lele.

220
00:12:41,660 --> 00:12:42,762
Hey, wait a minute.

221
00:12:42,762 --> 00:12:44,463
Sir, go back, that's the photo.

222
00:12:44,463 --> 00:12:46,098
Yes, look, that's me.

223
00:12:46,098 --> 00:12:48,768
The one in the black suit next to me is him.

224
00:12:49,769 --> 00:12:51,771
- It's you!
- No, it's not.

225
00:12:51,771 --> 00:12:55,741
Why on earth would a General Manager
send a secretary into the car?

226
00:12:55,741 --> 00:12:56,976
You made me misunderstand.

227
00:12:56,976 --> 00:12:58,210
I'm sorry.

228
00:12:58,210 --> 00:13:00,212
Why am I so unlucky?

229
00:13:03,048 --> 00:13:06,652
Alright, since it's a misunderstanding,

230
00:13:06,652 --> 00:13:07,653
Sir…

231
00:13:19,131 --> 00:13:22,501
Since your General Manager values you,

232
00:13:22,501 --> 00:13:24,270
his little secretary,

233
00:13:25,704 --> 00:13:26,739
well,

234
00:13:27,540 --> 00:13:30,242
would he be willing to pay a little more money?

235
00:13:33,078 --> 00:13:34,513
Value?

236
00:13:35,247 --> 00:13:38,584
Sir, this is a big misunderstanding.

237
00:13:38,584 --> 00:13:42,087
Our General Manager despises me.

238
00:13:43,222 --> 00:13:45,391
He always calls me clumsy.

239
00:13:45,391 --> 00:13:46,926
If I get one thing wrong,

240
00:13:46,926 --> 00:13:48,894
he tells me to stand
next to the plant in the office.

241
00:13:48,894 --> 00:13:49,929
Just stand there.

242
00:13:49,929 --> 00:13:53,199
He says all I need to do is breathe.

243
00:13:53,933 --> 00:13:59,171
He absolutely wouldn't pay a penny for me.

244
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:05,377
He might even hope that you would

245
00:14:05,377 --> 00:14:08,480
kill me on the spot.

246
00:14:10,115 --> 00:14:11,784
I'm done for.

247
00:14:18,190 --> 00:14:19,525
Sir.

248
00:14:19,525 --> 00:14:21,493
Before you end my life,

249
00:14:21,493 --> 00:14:24,029
could you give me something to eat first?

250
00:14:24,029 --> 00:14:25,564
I'm so hungry.

251
00:14:29,702 --> 00:14:32,137
Listen, in our line of work,

252
00:14:32,137 --> 00:14:34,540
it's long hours and high risk.

253
00:14:34,540 --> 00:14:35,841
The job is unstable,

254
00:14:35,841 --> 00:14:38,277
and we have to pay for gas and lunch money.

255
00:14:38,277 --> 00:14:39,678
There are no benefits at all.

256
00:14:46,452 --> 00:14:47,887
I'm sorry.

257
00:14:50,356 --> 00:14:51,991
Here.

258
00:15:02,234 --> 00:15:04,103
I don't know what it's stained with.

259
00:15:04,103 --> 00:15:05,571
The more I scrub, the dirtier it gets.

260
00:15:05,571 --> 00:15:06,624
Sorry.

261
00:15:10,209 --> 00:15:12,511
Maybe all bosses are like that.

262
00:15:15,514 --> 00:15:19,051
Actually, it's also tough for delivery staff.

263
00:15:19,051 --> 00:15:20,552
Once he glances over,

264
00:15:20,552 --> 00:15:21,887
I have to stand at attention

265
00:15:21,887 --> 00:15:23,222
and wait to be struck by lightning.

266
00:15:23,722 --> 00:15:25,190
This week I've been tormented

267
00:15:25,190 --> 00:15:27,026
into sleeping only three hours a day.

268
00:15:27,026 --> 00:15:28,260
I caught a cold,

269
00:15:28,260 --> 00:15:29,428
